        // --- Library ---
        'library_splash_title': 'Library Room',
        'library_splash_body': 'Here are your readings; this is where you hide your secret maps. Only captains who have completed successful missions can draw new treasure maps, so they are almost as rare as crystal books. Their value may be even greater. Of course there are many other maps too, with ordinary routes and guides; most people try to pass those off as treasure maps. Check them carefully—one might reveal another secret! Enjoy your time here!',
        'library_splash_ack_button': 'Got it, go on!',
